Package GoNature

Class Park

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.Park
  • public class Park
extends java.lang.Object
    Park represents a park in the system with details such as park name, current number of visitors, maximum capacity of visitors, and time limit for visitors. This class provides methods to retrieve and modify park details.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim, Nadine Halabi
